txt.en: You have destroyed several supply stores located throughout Gothmog's camp.\n\nYou should return to Dolenthol and inform him of your success.

'Scattered through the camp are several stockpiles of supplies. If we were to destroy these stores, we might cause sufficient distraction for us to withdraw from the area.\n\n'Would you see this done, friend? Venture deeper into the camp to create this distraction, and we will have our chance!'
Supply stores can be found throughout Gothmog's camp.\n\nYou should destroy the supply stores to create a distraction for Dolenthol.
'Thank you, [placeholder]. Your efforts will have created sufficient confusion for us to withdraw from the area.'
Gothmog's forces have several valuable supply stores located within their encampment. Dolenthol asked you to destroy the supplies, creating a distraction that might serve of some use to the Rangers.
